Pinch zoom gestures fully implemented. Zoom OUT increases min/max distances (150km max) with smaller labels. Zoom IN decreases distances (50m min) with larger labels. Labels disappear below minDistance threshold. Smooth transitions with reasonable bounds (0.3-3.0). All features working: gesture detection (MagnificationGesture), distance calculations, font scaling, display filtering. Comprehensive test coverage with 40+ zoom-related tests.
